-HERE FOR MY LESSON.

17:06.808 --> 17:07.983
-HOP IN!
-AFTER YOU.

17:09.028 --> 17:11.334
-NOW, THE TRICK IS NOT TO
LET MOMENTUM CARRY YOU AWAY.

17:11.464 --> 17:13.858
-DON'T LET THE
MOMENTUM CARRY ME AWAY.
-[LAUGHING]

17:13.989 --> 17:15.991
-BACK UP A LITTLE.
-OH BACK HERE, YEAH, OKAY.

17:16.122 --> 17:17.036
-NOW THESE CONTROLS ARE--

17:17.165 --> 17:18.079
-RIGHT HERE?

17:18.211 --> 17:19.429
-RIGHT.
-OKAY, GOT IT.

17:19.560 --> 17:20.517
-AND THIS CONTROLS
THE AIR FLOW.

17:20.647 --> 17:21.910
-OH, GREAT, I GOT IT, OKAY.

17:22.040 --> 17:23.172
-READY TO TAKE IT FOR A SPIN?

17:24.130 --> 17:25.000
-READY.

17:25.521 --> 17:26.741
-HELMETS, PLEASE.

17:27.481 --> 17:28.656
-OH, HELMETS.

17:31.006 --> 17:35.663
-[EXCITING ROCK MUSIC]

18:32.546 --> 18:33.982
-SO LET ME GET THIS STRAIGHT.

18:34.113 --> 18:37.028
YOU AND THE LIFEGUARD
WANNA PLAY ALEX AND ME?

18:37.159 --> 18:38.508
-LOOK, HERE IT IS.

18:38.639 --> 18:40.597
IF YOU GUYS WIN, OUR
PARTNERSHIP'S OVER

18:40.728 --> 18:41.946
WITH NO HARD FEELINGS.

18:42.077 --> 18:44.035
BUT IF WE WIN,
ALEX TAKES A HIKE,

18:44.166 --> 18:45.167
AND YOU AND I PLAY TOGETHER.

18:45.298 --> 18:46.995
-WHY WOULD I AGREE TO THAT?

18:47.126 --> 18:48.344
-WHAT, ARE YOU
WORRIED ABOUT LOSING

18:48.475 --> 18:50.216
TO THE WALKING WOUNDED
AND AN AMATEUR?

18:50.346 --> 18:52.696
-GIVE ME A BREAK.
-SO WHAT'S YOUR PROBLEM?

18:53.306 --> 18:54.568
-NO ONE'S TALKING TO YOU.

18:54.698 --> 18:56.787
-HEY BROYLES, YOU
BETTER BE NICE TO HIM.

18:56.918 --> 18:58.963
WHEN WE BEAT YOU,
YOU'RE GONNA HAVE TO BEG
MATT TO PLAY WITH YOU.

18:59.094 --> 19:00.530
-NEVER HAPPEN.

19:01.618 --> 19:02.619
-SO WHAT DO YOU SAY, KURT?

19:02.750 --> 19:04.099
DO WE SETTLE THIS ON THE COURT?

19:05.274 --> 19:06.188
-OKAY, WHEN?

19:06.797 --> 19:08.582
-TOMORROW MORNING
BEFORE THE TOURNAMENT.

19:08.712 --> 19:09.844
-WE'LL BE HERE.

19:10.627 --> 19:11.628
-SO WILL WE.

19:11.759 --> 19:13.152
-HEY BROYLES.
-YEAH.

19:14.718 --> 19:15.589
GOOD REFLEXES.

19:15.719 --> 19:17.156
-HEY MAN, DON'T MESS WITH ME.

19:17.286 --> 19:18.461
-SAVE IT FOR TOMORROW.

19:18.592 --> 19:19.419
-[LAUGHING]

19:21.029 --> 19:23.379
-ALL RIGHT, WORK ON
THE SPIKE, BANG IT DOWN.

19:23.510 --> 19:24.902
NOBODY, NOBODY, NOBODY!

19:25.033 --> 19:27.340
NICE HIT, MAN, ALL RIGHT
GET BACK THERE, COME ON.

19:28.341 --> 19:31.648
ANGLE, ANGLE, ANGLE, ANGLE,
ANGLE, ANGLE! OKAY! NICE HEAT!

19:31.779 --> 19:33.694
ALL RIGHT, LOOKING
STRONG, LOOKING STRONG.

19:33.824 --> 19:35.565
DON'T WORRY ABOUT
THAT, THAT'S OKAY,

19:35.696 --> 19:36.523
YOU'RE NOT TIRED YET, ARE YOU?

19:37.915 --> 19:39.178
DEEP LINE, DEEP LINE,
DEEP LINE!

19:40.091 --> 19:42.050
HIT LINE, HIT LINE,
HIT LINE, NICE.

19:42.181 --> 19:43.486
ALL RIGHT HERE YOU GO.

19:43.617 --> 19:45.619
STAY LOW, STAY LOW,
STAY LOW, THERE YOU GO.

19:45.749 --> 19:47.316
NICE PLAY, NICE PLAY.

19:47.447 --> 19:48.665
LEAN FORWARD, LEAN FORWARD,

19:48.796 --> 19:50.319
ON YOUR TOES, ON YOUR TOES,

19:50.450 --> 19:52.016
HANDS OUT IN FRONT OF YOU,
HANDS OUT IN FRONT OF YOU.

19:52.147 --> 19:53.322
HERE YOU GO, WAIT FOR IT,
ON YOUR TOES, ON YOUR TOES.

19:53.453 --> 19:55.106
HERE COMES ONE DOWN THE LINE.

19:55.237 --> 19:56.630
HANDS OUT IN FRONT OF YOU,
HANDS OUT IN FRONT OF YOU,

19:56.760 --> 19:57.805
HERE YOU GO, DIG THE
BALL, DIG THE BALL,

19:57.935 --> 19:58.980
