-SHOULDN'T WE GET
THIS OUT OF HIM?

34:40.600 --> 34:42.080
-NO. WE'VE GOTTA GET
HIM TO A HOSPITAL.

34:42.210 --> 34:43.429
-COAST GUARD HELOS
