-GO GO!
-GO GO GO GO!

36:27.010 --> 36:28.011
COME ON, GO GO GO!

36:29.926 --> 36:34.975
-[SIREN BLARING]

37:18.497 --> 37:19.367
-ALL RIGHT.

37:19.889 --> 37:20.977
BE CAREFUL, BE CAREFUL.

37:21.108 --> 37:22.979
READY ON THREE,
ONE, TWO, THREE.

37:23.110 --> 37:23.980
OKAY.

37:27.201 --> 37:28.942
ALL RIGHT, LET'S HEAD
HIM IN, HEAD HIM IN.

37:29.072 --> 37:30.030
-WATCH YOUR FOOTING.

37:31.640 --> 37:32.467
-EASY, EASY.

37:34.121 --> 37:35.731
ALL RIGHT, GO GO GO GO GO!

37:40.040 --> 37:41.041
GO GO!

37:44.523 --> 37:46.220
I'M REALLY GLAD
YOU DIDN'T LEAVE.

37:46.351 --> 37:48.222
-SOMETHING TOLD
ME I'D BETTER STAY.

37:55.055 --> 37:57.710
I WANT TO SKY DIVE,
BICYCLE THROUGH FRANCE,

37:57.840 --> 37:59.538
ACT IN A BROADWAY SHOW,

37:59.668 --> 38:01.540
MEET BOB DYLAN, ALL
SORTS OF THINGS.

38:02.149 --> 38:03.498
-MARRIAGE? KIDS?

38:04.194 --> 38:05.239
-NO, NOT FOR ME.

38:05.370 --> 38:06.458
THERE'S TOO MUCH
ELSE I WANNA DO.

38:07.154 --> 38:10.157
-AFTER YOU GIVE EVERY
SINGLE LIFEGUARD AT BAYWATCH

38:10.288 --> 38:12.638
EXTENSIVE TRAINING ON
OUR NEW HOVERCRAFT.

38:12.768 --> 38:13.987
SHOULD TAKE MONTHS.

38:14.509 --> 38:16.468
-I ACCEPTED CAPTAIN
RUSSELL'S OFFER TO WORK HERE,

38:16.598 --> 38:19.122
BUT ONLY UNTIL LIEUTENANT
HOLDEN GETS BACK.

38:20.341 --> 38:21.299
-THAT SHOULD BE LONG ENOUGH.

38:22.387 --> 38:24.171
-SAID THE SPIDER TO THE FLY.

38:24.302 --> 38:26.304
-DON'T YOU JUST
LOVE SPIDER WEBS

38:26.434 --> 38:28.306
WITH BEADS OF DEW ON
THEM IN THE MORNING?

38:28.436 --> 38:31.352
-[LAUGHING] YES, AND I STILL THINK THAT
PEOPLE WHO WORK TOGETHER

38:31.483 --> 38:33.963
SHOULD NOT GET INVOLVED.
IT COMPLICATES EVERYTHING.

38:34.094 --> 38:36.792
-WELL, I DON'T KNOW.
COMPLICATIONS ARE
THE SPICE OF LIFE.

38:36.923 --> 38:39.621
-I THOUGHT YOU DIDN'T
LIKE COMPLICATIONS OR SALT.

38:39.752 --> 38:41.188
-[LAUGHING]

38:43.669 --> 38:44.496
THINGS CHANGE.

38:45.105 --> 38:46.541
-[LAUGHING]

38:48.717 --> 38:50.502
-THEN ALEX BEGGED
ME TO BE HIS PARTNER.

38:50.632 --> 38:52.068
I MEAN IT WAS GREAT, I LOVED IT.

38:52.939 --> 38:55.507
-MATT, ARE YOU GONNA
JOIN THE TOUR OR NOT?

38:55.637 --> 38:59.162
-NOT. THEY TRAVEL ALL AROUND
THE COUNTRY IN ARENAS

38:59.293 --> 39:00.642
AND FAKE SAND COURTS.

39:00.773 --> 39:02.383
I WANNA BE HERE
ON THE REAL BEACH.

39:02.905 --> 39:05.081
AND I ALSO WANNA
BE HERE NEAR YOU.

39:06.300 --> 39:08.084
I JUST WANTED TO TRY TO
SEE IF I COULD DO IT.

39:08.824 --> 39:10.522
-OKAY, AS LONG AS
TEN YEARS FROM NOW

39:10.652 --> 39:12.437
YOU DON'T HAVE SOME KIND OF
MID LIFE CRISIS ABOUT IT.

39:12.567 --> 39:15.091
-HEY, IF I DO, I'LL
TAKE AFTER GARNER

39:15.222 --> 39:16.919
AND DEAL WITH IT THEN.
-LADIES AND GENTLEMEN,

39:17.050 --> 39:19.444
PLEASE WELCOME A
MAN THAT I BELIEVE

39:19.574 --> 39:21.402
WAS BORN TO SING THE BLUES,

39:21.533 --> 39:23.491
MR. GARNER ELLERBEE.

39:25.928 --> 39:27.626
-GO GARNER, LET'S GO!

39:27.756 --> 39:28.583
WHOO!

39:28.714 --> 39:32.805
-[APPLAUDING]

39:43.729 --> 39:46.471
[END MUSIC PLAYING]
